<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201022/be422e9a2c134229acabf656c7ee7486.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> “我要扼住命运的咽喉,</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 决不能让命运使我屈服。”</strong></p>
